利用和角公式导出
(a)cos(x - pi/2) = sinx
	if a = pi/2
	cos(x - pi/2) = cos(x - b) = cos(x)*cos(-b) - sin(x)*sin(-b)
	cos(-pi/2) = 0
	sin(-pi/2) = -1
	=>cos(x - pi/2) = sin(x)

(b)cos(A - B) = cos(A)*cos(B) + sin(A)*sin(B)
	cos(A+(-B)) = cos(A)*cos(-B) - sin(A)*sin(-B)
	cos(-B) = cos(B)
	sin(-B) = -sin(B)
	=>cos(A - B) = cos(A)*cos(B) + sin(A)*sin(B)
